snippet.title: ALONE... Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Alone is a Handcrafted iOS and Android game about flying through space in a lone-piloted vessel, navigating caves, ripping through rocky outcrops, dodging falling debris and surviving ever more claustrophobic worlds.

iPhone iTunes $1.99
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/alone.../id848515450?ls=1&mt=8

Android Google Play $1.99:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.laserdog.alone

www.alone-game.com

ALONE by Laser Dog Games
